Actress Halima Abubakar has explained she produces her movies to avoid s3x-for- roles demand in the industry. The producer stated this on her official Twitter handle days after returning to micro-blogging platform. “I left Twitter, not Nollywood . I produce my own movies. I no get strength for s3x,” she tweeted.   Tana Adelana loses dad     Nse Ikpe-Etim: I’m not ashamed I don’t have children     FRANK EDOHO: Why I dumped rap for broadcasting   She also explained why she took a break. “Taking a break is necessary. I have won all the awards so I won’t be too hungry to ass lick or belong to a group. Like I said before, I don’t have a filter, I say the truth , I mean that’s me,” she tweeted.